    FAIL  ERB.T31_g35.ICN.jaguar.compare.ccsm4_0_alpha36 
    FAIL  ERH.f19_f19.F.jaguar.compare.ccsm4_0_alpha36 
    FAIL  ERS.f19_g15.B18C.jaguar.compare.ccsm4_0_alpha36 
